TITLE: Processing Old PREVOTE Messages in PBTS
DESCRIPTION: Handler for processing previous round PREVOTE messages, ensuring value consistency across rounds with different proposed times.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cometbft/cometbft/blob/main/spec/consensus/proposer-based-timestamp/v1/pbts-algorithm_001_draft.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: go
CODE:
```
upon timely(PROPOSAL, h_p, round_p, (v, tprop), vr) from proposer(h_p, round_p) AND 2f + 1 PREVOTE, h_p, vr, id((v, tvote) 
while step_p = propose  (vr  0  vr < round_p) do {
  if valid(v)  (lockedRound_p  vr  lockedValue_p = v) {
    broadcast PREVOTE, h_p, roundp, id(v, tprop)
  }
  else {
    broadcast PREVOTE, hp, roundp, nil
  }
  step_p  prevote
}
```

