TITLE: Defining the BlockID Structure in CometBFT
DESCRIPTION: Defines the `BlockID` structure in CometBFT. It contains two distinct Merkle roots: the header hash (`Hash`) and the hash of the block parts (`PartSetHeader`), along with the total number of parts implicitly via the PartSetHeader. Both hash components have specific validation requirements.
