[CMBC-ATTACK.1]

If there exists three light blocks a, b, and c, with
*sign-skip-match(a,b,c,t) = false* then we have an *attack*.  We say
we have **an attack at height** *b.Header.Height* and write
*attack(a,b,c,t)*.
```

